Package Ensemble

Class MathsEnsemble<T>

java.lang.Object
Ensemble.MathsEnsemble<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the elements of the set
All Implemented Interfaces:
Ensemble<T>
public class MathsEnsemble<T> extends Object implements Ensemble<T>
This class implements a mathematical set of objects. It implements the Ensemble interface. It uses a LinkedHashSet to store the elements of the set.
